column5: 2 friend while packing up their truck in the Niagara Glen parking lot forgot their rods and reels behind.  One thought the other put them away.  Lesson learned the hard way.  Any info if you found please PM myself.  RPX 13'6, Gold Islander, Quantum rod, Blue Islander  Thanks
Nuts...thought this post was that maybe you found my lost rods and reels! Hope you guys have better luck than me.
